==Arabic alphabet==

===Letter===
{{ARchar|'''د '''/''' ‍د'''}} (dāl)

# The eighth letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[خ]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ذ]]}}.
# The fourth letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ج]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ه]]}}.

